}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "M01-D6505-D10" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. :The FCC sample label has a MAC with a CC:5D:4E ('''[[ZyXEL]]''') OUI. The FCC ID of the parent product (MQ4NWD6505F, '''[[AboCom]]''' NWD6505F) :has also been assigned to this entry. This device is using [[MediaTek MT7610U]] (MT7610UN). :{{WiFiCert|WFA20064|06/21/2013}}
Per '''[[ZyXEL]]''''s driver, the USB ID for this device is '''0586:3425''' :The device description in the driver is <small>'''ZyXEL Dual-Band Wireless AC600 USB Adapter'''</small>.
Additional specifications, per '''ZyXEL''''s product page, follow... *Power consumption: 1.25 W *Item dimensions (W x D x H): 58 mm x 21 mm x 11 mm *Item weight: 8 g
